## 7. Quick reference

| Method | Path | Auth | Request body | Response |
|--------|------|------|--------------|----------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | no | `LoginBody` | `LoginResponse` |
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | no | `RegisterBody` | `RegisterResponse` |
| POST | `/api/auth/forgot-password` | no | `ForgotPasswordBody` | `ForgotPasswordResponse` |
| POST | `/api/auth/reset-password` | no | `ResetPasswordBody` | `ResetPasswordResponse` |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | JWT | — | `UserProfile` |
| PATCH | `/api/auth/me/password` | JWT | `UpdatePasswordBody` | — |
| GET | `/api/endpoints` | JWT | — | `Endpoint[]` |
| POST | `/api/endpoints` | JWT | `CreateEndpointBody` | `Endpoint` |
| GET | `/api/endpoints/:id` | JWT | — | `Endpoint` |
| DELETE | `/api/endpoints/:id` | JWT | — | 204 |
| GET | `/api/requests?endpointId=&limit=&offset=` | JWT | — | `RequestsListResponse` |
| GET | `/api/requests/:id` | JWT | — | `RequestItem` |
| DELETE | `/api/requests/:id` | JWT | — | 204 |
| POST | `/api/hooks/:token` | no | any | `WebhookResponse` |

